653
00:56:20,500 --> 00:56:23,570


654
00:56:23,570 --> 00:56:26,730


655
00:56:26,730 --> 00:56:29,970


656
00:56:29,970 --> 00:56:33,180
She's taking the document!

657
00:56:33,180 --> 00:56:36,090


658
00:56:36,090 --> 00:56:39,240
No!

659
00:56:39,240 --> 00:56:42,310


660
00:56:42,310 --> 00:56:45,540


661
00:56:45,540 --> 00:56:49,690


662
00:56:49,690 --> 00:56:53,210
All individuals present must come out and pay their respects.

663
00:56:57,390 --> 00:56:58,900


664
00:57:46,080 --> 00:57:48,770
My goodness.

665
00:57:50,410 --> 00:57:54,350


666
00:57:58,560 --> 00:58:01,040
I am here for official business.

667
00:58:01,980 --> 00:58:05,030
- Begin the search! <br>- Yes, Sir!

668
00:58:21,470 --> 00:58:24,000
A secret inspector is here!

669
00:58:26,130 --> 00:58:29,700
Out of all days, why did the secret inspector come today?

670
00:58:31,730 --> 00:58:33,920
Am I the only one that sees that the numbers do not match?

671
00:58:33,920 --> 00:58:36,870
Even an illiterate person can see that the numbers are not adding up.

672
00:58:36,870 --> 00:58:41,770
There are three more carts filled with documents in the storage.

673
00:58:43,050 --> 00:58:46,770
Criminals are never guilty of just one crime.

674
00:58:56,900 --> 00:58:58,700
Listen here, Magistrate Jang Gi Wan.

675
00:58:58,700 --> 00:59:02,390
Forgive me for interrupting but there is something I must say.

676
00:59:02,390 --> 00:59:05,150
Please forgive me for my crimes.

677
00:59:05,150 --> 00:59:09,150
I am nothing but a corrupt magistrate who abused his power.

678
00:59:12,210 --> 00:59:15,990
Why are you confessing when I did not ask?

679
00:59:15,990 --> 00:59:19,340
You were going to find out anyway.

680
00:59:19,340 --> 00:59:20,760
Please punish me.

681
00:59:20,760 --> 00:59:24,840
No. Please, take me to Hanyang.

682
00:59:28,330 --> 00:59:33,720
The right punishment for you will be decided when I review all the fabricated documents and report it to His Majesty.

683
00:59:33,720 --> 00:59:35,910
Your punishment will not be discussed now.

684
00:59:35,910 --> 00:59:42,720
In addition to that, the crime I am charging you of has nothing to do with corruption or abuse.

685
00:59:42,720 --> 00:59:44,640
This is a murder charge.

686
00:59:52,670 --> 00:59:57,190
An inspector, Park Moo Gyeong, was investigating the missing grains and military supplies from here.

687
00:59:57,190 --> 01:00:01,850
He suddenly disappeared after sending his report.

688
01:00:01,850 --> 01:00:08,020
However, after finding his body, you ordered it to be abandoned.

689
01:00:08,020 --> 01:00:12,200
Why? To hide the cause of death.

690
01:00:12,200 --> 01:00:16,080
No. I only did that to identify the man.

691
01:00:16,080 --> 01:00:19,220
That is the only reason I brought him here.

692
01:00:19,220 --> 01:00:20,950
Bring him out.

693
01:00:29,990 --> 01:00:35,110
This horse pass was found on the corpse.

694
01:00:35,110 --> 01:00:39,630
Was the Magistrate aware that the deceased man was an inspector?

695
01:00:39,630 --> 01:00:42,320
<i>My Lord! My Lord!</i>

696
01:00:42,320 --> 01:00:46,120
<i>The dead body of the inspector was found in the ocean.</i>

697
01:00:46,120 --> 01:00:47,570
<i>What?</i>

698
01:00:47,570 --> 01:00:50,230
Yes, he was aware of this.

699
01:00:50,230 --> 01:00:51,850
That is a lie.

700
01:00:51,850 --> 01:00:54,390
I was not aware.

701
01:00:54,390 --> 01:00:56,370
Bring him out.

702
01:00:59,990 --> 01:01:03,330
Did you hear what he said in front of the dead body?

703
01:01:03,330 --> 01:01:05,190
Yes.

704
01:01:07,060 --> 01:01:13,510
<i>I made sure that we took care of this along with the sunken vessel.</i>

705
01:01:13,510 --> 01:01:15,540
Take care of it?

706
01:01:16,460 --> 01:01:18,200
What exactly is it that you took care of?

707
01:01:18,200 --> 01:01:22,090
Were you talking about sinking the vessel and killing the secret inspector?

708
01:01:22,090 --> 01:01:25,330
No! I did not murder anyone!

709
01:01:25,330 --> 01:01:28,550
Then you must have sunk the vessel.

710
01:01:29,560 --> 01:01:32,480
T-t-that's not how it is.

711
01:01:44,230 --> 01:01:47,130
Do you know what this is?

712
01:01:47,130 --> 01:01:51,400
How would I know?

713
01:01:53,030 --> 01:01:55,500
This is black pine, an expensive wood...

714
01:01:55,500 --> 01:02:00,470
It is only used to make vessels that transport products for the king.

715
01:02:00,470 --> 01:02:03,830
It was found where the body resurfaced.

716
01:02:06,020 --> 01:02:10,750
<i>In this region, vessels rarely capsize.</i>

717
01:02:10,750 --> 01:02:13,130
<i>It seems as though</i>

718
01:02:13,130 --> 01:02:16,220
<i>someone made the hole intentionally.</i>

719
01:02:16,220 --> 01:02:18,000
<i>Look here.</i>

720
01:02:19,300 --> 01:02:22,460
You feared that all your corrupt deeds would be revealed,

721
01:02:22,460 --> 01:02:27,350
so you killed Park Moo Gyeong who was sent to inspect this region.

722
01:02:30,280 --> 01:02:35,870
Also, to cover this fact, you sunk the vessel.

723
01:02:36,920 --> 01:02:39,760
Regardless of everything, the body washed up...

724
01:02:39,760 --> 01:02:41,730
So you tried to dispose of it!

725
01:02:41,730 --> 01:02:44,550
I swear that I did not kill him.

726
01:02:44,550 --> 01:02:49,100
Even if you did not see to it yourself, you covered it up.

727
01:02:49,100 --> 01:02:52,280
You do not need to hold a knife to take a life.

728
01:02:57,710 --> 01:02:59,020
This is an order!

729
01:02:59,020 --> 01:03:02,520
- Lock the storage and take the seal! <br> - Yes, Sir!

730
01:03:02,520 --> 01:03:05,800
Take the seal? My document has not been signed yet.

731
01:03:05,800 --> 01:03:09,860
Who dares to speak?!

732
01:03:10,590 --> 01:03:12,780
He cannot take the seal.

733
01:03:12,780 --> 01:03:15,680
Jang Gi Wan is to be put in prison.

734
01:03:15,680 --> 01:03:19,770
Until the investigation ends, no one is allowed to enter!

735
01:03:19,770 --> 01:03:21,990
That cannot be!

736
01:03:27,040 --> 01:03:29,690
You... you are the one that assaulted...

737
01:03:29,690 --> 01:03:31,880
You're Bang Deuk!

738
01:03:36,210 --> 01:03:42,000
Secret Royal Inspector, Sir... The thing is...

739
01:03:42,890 --> 01:03:44,210
I must have been crazy.

740
01:03:44,210 --> 01:03:47,190
That time, I really thought you were a beggar.

741
01:03:47,190 --> 01:03:51,480
You looked penniless, homeless, and...

742
01:03:51,480 --> 01:03:54,800
Anyway, I am aware that I should die for my insolence but

743
01:03:54,800 --> 01:03:57,030
- My Lord! <br> - Mother!

744
01:03:57,030 --> 01:04:01,760
Please just put this wench in prison.

745
01:04:01,760 --> 01:04:04,920
This is worthless!

746
01:04:07,970 --> 01:04:09,640
The Magistrate..

747
01:04:09,640 --> 01:04:11,990
Did not even stamp his seal.

748
01:04:14,090 --> 01:04:17,040
Here you go, you wench.

749
01:04:19,460 --> 01:04:22,960
You arrived at the perfect time, Royal Inspector.

750
01:04:22,960 --> 01:04:26,540
I pray that you live a long and healthy life.

751
01:04:26,540 --> 01:04:30,950
Then, we will return home.

752
01:04:30,950 --> 01:04:32,590
You shameless thing.

753
01:04:32,590 --> 01:04:35,560
You are audacious to no end.

754
01:04:37,090 --> 01:04:38,850
Let go of her.

755
01:04:38,850 --> 01:04:42,840
How dare you use violence in a governement office?

756
01:04:48,140 --> 01:04:51,130
I hope I'm not too late.

